WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:00.370 --> 00:00:03.570
Extend your hand, no need to fear

3
00:00:03.780 --> 00:00:06.740
Cut through the wind, and persevere

4
00:00:07.070 --> 00:00:11.410
Chart your own course, the time to push forward is here

5
00:00:16.390 --> 00:00:19.710
In a time like a storm, hear the tidal waves roar,

6
00:00:19.710 --> 00:00:22.750
we keep trudging along but we're still wanting more

7
00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:26.260
But in spite of it all, the foundation we built

8
00:00:26.260 --> 00:00:28.880
for ourselves was about to fall

9
00:00:29.470 --> 00:00:32.760
Where the compass points - Is it right? Is it wrong?

10
00:00:32.760 --> 00:00:35.470
Who to ask? As if there's anyone listening

11
00:00:35.830 --> 00:00:38.810
I guess you'll never be one hundred percent sure

12
00:00:39.310 --> 00:00:42.270
But if you shut your eyes to the chaos,

13
00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:45.400
and you'd only take a breath

14
00:00:45.820 --> 00:00:48.700
When you open up your eyes

15
00:00:49.070 --> 00:00:52.410
you will find where you were meant to be

16
00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:55.830
Extend your hand, no need to fear

17
00:00:55.990 --> 00:00:59.040
Cut through the wind, and persevere

18
00:00:59.310 --> 00:01:03.920
Kick out the dark until the sky clears

19
00:01:05.210 --> 00:01:08.090
Even as we act in our own best interests,

20
00:01:08.260 --> 00:01:11.930
doing what we each believe is for our own

21
00:01:12.390 --> 00:01:16.720
Chart your own course, the time to push forward is here

22
00:01:30.030 --> 00:01:35.950
<b>Banquet Hall


Third Floor


Inside

the Castle</b>

23
00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:35.950
Now then, I've got some samurai to snuff out.

24
00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:41.080
But before that, I ought to
finish the job at hand.

25
00:01:42.370 --> 00:01:46.750
Caiman Lady, are you ready to broadcast
his voice all over the island?

26
00:01:46.750 --> 00:01:48.130
Yes, I am!

27
00:01:48.130 --> 00:01:49.840
Black Leg...

28
00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:53.260
Would you kindly summon
Nico Robin at once?

29
00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:58.010
We're all ready to go...

30
00:01:58.060 --> 00:02:04.150
<b>The Honorable Hyogoro "the Flower"</b>

31
00:01:58.430 --> 00:02:01.430
I've set up layers of webbing
all around the entrance.

32
00:02:01.430 --> 00:02:05.650
Once you've touched my sticky,
hard gum, you'll never escape.

33
00:02:06.770 --> 00:02:08.440
I've coated the floor as well.

34
00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:10.400
One wrong step and you're trapped.

35
00:02:11.820 --> 00:02:17.120
On top of that, my girls are standing guard
with tranquilizer guns in the back.

36
00:02:18.530 --> 00:02:20.870
All that's left for you to do...

37
00:02:27.130 --> 00:02:29.960
is call out for her!

38
00:02:30.710 --> 00:02:31.960
Call Nico Robin!

39
00:02:35.430 --> 00:02:38.600
Come on, call for help!

40
00:02:38.600 --> 00:02:40.600
I have another matter to attend to!

41
00:02:44.230 --> 00:02:45.230
Robin...

42
00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:50.570
I want... to join your crew.

43
00:02:50.570 --> 00:02:51.900
– Huh?!
– Huh?!

44
00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:53.280
I...

45
00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:54.700
I...

46
00:02:57.530 --> 00:03:00.160
I want to live!

47
00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:06.620
You sure are stubborn...

48
00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:11.550
Come on! Come on! Come on!

49
00:03:11.550 --> 00:03:13.380
Oh, I can't watch...

50
00:03:13.380 --> 00:03:14.760
I'm going to cry...

51
00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:18.890
That man won't let his friend come to harm!

52
00:03:18.890 --> 00:03:22.010
He'd rather die than utter a single word!

53
00:03:22.010 --> 00:03:25.890
If he wasn't our enemy,
I might have fallen in love!

54
00:03:25.890 --> 00:03:27.850
W-Wait!

55
00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:37.990
Give me a minute...

56
00:03:37.990 --> 00:03:41.160
to say a few words...

57
00:03:42.030 --> 00:03:47.420
I bet he just wants to say something
like "eat shit" before he dies!

58
00:03:47.420 --> 00:03:48.540
Please don't!

59
00:03:48.540 --> 00:03:52.000
Don't make her any angrier, or else...

60
00:03:52.340 --> 00:03:54.010
Robin...

61
00:03:54.010 --> 00:03:56.800
I... I...

62
00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.800
I...

63
00:03:58.470 --> 00:04:02.510
wanted to see your smile... one more time...

64
00:04:08.060 --> 00:04:13.400
Help me, Robin!

65
00:04:16.190 --> 00:04:20.280
– What?!
– What?!

66
00:04:17.950 --> 00:04:20.280
He called her for help after all!

67
00:04:23.740 --> 00:04:25.120
I'm on the third floor!

68
00:04:25.750 --> 00:04:27.960
In the banquet hall!

69
00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:29.750
I've been taken hostage!

70
00:04:29.750 --> 00:04:30.750
I'm sorry!

71
00:04:31.540 --> 00:04:32.670
Sanji...

72
00:04:33.130 --> 00:04:37.590
They're gonna kill me
if you don't come, Robin!

73
00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:40.640
Help!

74
00:04:41.590 --> 00:04:44.640
What the hell is that? Talk about pathetic!

75
00:04:44.640 --> 00:04:47.270
Is that one of the Straw Hats?!

76
00:04:47.270 --> 00:04:51.400
Listen to that! His voice is echoing
across the entire island!

77
00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:59.240
Nico Robin is one of the most
important figures in the world.

78
00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:02.320
They must be after her knowledge!

79
00:05:04.740 --> 00:05:09.120
Sounds to me like an obvious trap for Robin!

80
00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:12.710
Those are some pretty pathetic
sounds coming from a man!

81
00:05:20.420 --> 00:05:22.470
These guys are a riot!

82
00:05:22.470 --> 00:05:25.140
I'd bet anything it's a woman.

83
00:05:25.470 --> 00:05:26.970
What a pain...

84
00:05:26.970 --> 00:05:30.810
Hey, Nami! His voice is coming from up there!

85
00:05:30.810 --> 00:05:32.020
Be careful!

86
00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:34.190
I saw one of those earlier!

87
00:05:33.060 --> 00:05:36.070
You're my only hope!

88
00:05:34.190 --> 00:05:36.070
What's with that eye?

89
00:05:36.070 --> 00:05:37.690
Come quickly!

90
00:05:37.690 --> 00:05:42.030
Robin!

91
00:05:47.330 --> 00:05:48.790
What a surprise.

92
00:05:54.460 --> 00:05:56.540
I called for Robin.

93
00:05:56.540 --> 00:05:58.630
Now, untie me.

94
00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:02.090
What?!

95
00:06:03.050 --> 00:06:06.050
Madame, someone's coming!

96
00:06:06.050 --> 00:06:07.970
Already, huh?

97
00:06:07.970 --> 00:06:10.850
You're not going anywhere.

98
00:06:10.850 --> 00:06:12.020
Huh?!

99
00:06:12.020 --> 00:06:14.730
Didn't you say you loved me?

100
00:06:14.730 --> 00:06:17.900
Well, that means this isn't business anymore.

101
00:06:17.900 --> 00:06:19.440
Now it's personal.

102
00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:21.490
See those boys?

103
00:06:21.490 --> 00:06:24.070
You'll be one of my precious
pets, just like them.

104
00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:33.960
You won't be able to live without
my touch once I'm through with you.

105
00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:37.380
– My heart belongs to Madame Black Maria alone...
– My heart belongs to Madame Black Maria alone...

106
00:06:38.380 --> 00:06:39.380
My heart...

107
00:06:39.750 --> 00:06:42.210
belongs to all the ladies!

108
00:06:42.210 --> 00:06:44.760
I forbid you to be unfaithful to me!

109
00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:46.180
You need to be disciplined!

110
00:06:46.180 --> 00:06:47.300
Hold on!

111
00:06:47.300 --> 00:06:52.140
I wouldn't want to hurt a lady,
so my armament haki is going soft!

112
00:06:53.020 --> 00:06:54.390
Mil Fleurs!

113
00:06:57.480 --> 00:06:59.320
Gigantesco Mano!

114
00:06:59.980 --> 00:07:00.650
Spank!

115
00:07:07.320 --> 00:07:08.910
Madame Black Maria!

116
00:07:18.710 --> 00:07:21.300
How did you get in here?!

117
00:07:24.050 --> 00:07:25.930
I can bloom anywhere.

118
00:07:28.510 --> 00:07:30.510
How dare you strike my face...

119
00:07:31.220 --> 00:07:36.440
You really thought I'd be so naive
as to walk straight into your trap?

120
00:07:37.100 --> 00:07:39.480
Robin!

121
00:07:46.950 --> 00:07:50.070
I spent a lot of time in
nefarious organizations.

122
00:07:50.870 --> 00:07:54.000
When someone torments my friends...

123
00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:56.160
I can't contain...

124
00:07:56.870 --> 00:07:59.250
the devil within me!

125
00:08:05.130 --> 00:08:06.510
Ah, pardon me!

126
00:08:06.510 --> 00:08:09.260
I've cut you free with
the icy chill of the underworld.

127
00:08:10.930 --> 00:08:11.970
Brook!

128
00:08:16.390 --> 00:08:19.690
Miss! They took down the tranquilizer unit!

129
00:08:19.690 --> 00:08:21.360
All your spider silk traps...

130
00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:23.520
...have been frozen and shattered, too!

131
00:08:25.530 --> 00:08:30.160
It seems as though spider silk and the chill
of the underworld go well together!

132
00:08:35.540 --> 00:08:38.160
Monsters!

133
00:08:38.160 --> 00:08:39.750
– Look who's talking!
– Look who's talking!

134
00:08:41.040 --> 00:08:42.420
Thank you!

135
00:08:42.420 --> 00:08:44.130
You saved me...

136
00:08:44.130 --> 00:08:46.000
Think nothing of it.

137
00:08:46.590 --> 00:08:51.010
Sorry about this, but I'm gonna go
lend a hand to Kin'emon's group!

138
00:08:52.970 --> 00:08:56.310
For some reason, I just can't
see myself winning this one!

139
00:08:56.680 --> 00:08:57.850
– You don't say.
– You don't say.

140
00:08:57.850 --> 00:08:59.640
Get back here, Black Leg!

141
00:08:59.640 --> 00:09:01.650
You're going to be my pet!

142
00:09:01.650 --> 00:09:02.900
I won't let you go!

143
00:09:03.940 --> 00:09:04.940
Is that all?

144
00:09:10.070 --> 00:09:11.280
Any more last words?

145
00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:23.170
You'd die to save a man
who'd sell out his own friends?

146
00:09:23.170 --> 00:09:26.000
No, Black Maria...

147
00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:28.840
It seems you fail to understand...

148
00:09:32.030 --> 00:09:34.510
just how wonderful friends can be.

149
00:09:36.760 --> 00:09:37.720
Sanji!

150
00:09:40.230 --> 00:09:42.650
Thank you for relying on me!

151
00:09:42.650 --> 00:09:44.150
It makes me happy!

152
00:09:46.770 --> 00:09:47.730
Ah, watch out.

153
00:09:48.150 --> 00:09:49.490
The floor is frozen.

154
00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:56.030
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

155
00:09:56.030 --> 00:09:57.870
Thank you!

156
00:09:58.450 --> 00:10:02.370
<b>Forbidden Storeroom

Inside the Dome</b>

157
00:10:05.880 --> 00:10:08.250
Why would there be smoke
coming out of a mouse?

158
00:10:08.250 --> 00:10:12.760
It's one of the Marys, the surveillance
unit of my father's army.

159
00:10:12.760 --> 00:10:13.800
It's a cyborg.

160
00:10:14.140 --> 00:10:17.850
In other words, an animal with
mechanical body parts.

161
00:10:17.850 --> 00:10:19.100
What?!

162
00:10:20.060 --> 00:10:23.440
They wander around the island aimlessly,

163
00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:26.940
but they share what they
see with the human Marys!

164
00:10:26.940 --> 00:10:27.690
– What?!
– What?!

165
00:10:28.230 --> 00:10:29.780
So, even in here...

166
00:10:35.780 --> 00:10:37.990
Hey, are you sure it's this storehouse?

167
00:10:37.990 --> 00:10:41.450
This place is cursed. No one
goes in there anymore.

168
00:10:41.870 --> 00:10:45.420
It doesn't look like anyone went inside.

169
00:10:45.420 --> 00:10:47.330
But they said this was the place!

170
00:10:47.330 --> 00:10:49.210
There's no doubt about it!

171
00:10:49.210 --> 00:10:50.300
Young Master Yamato–

172
00:10:50.300 --> 00:10:52.380
I mean, the next shogun is in there!

173
00:10:52.380 --> 00:10:54.430
It sounds like there are many of them.

174
00:10:54.430 --> 00:10:56.760
This place isn't safe anymore!

175
00:10:56.760 --> 00:10:58.680
We must flee, Yamato!

176
00:10:58.680 --> 00:11:02.140
Please show us a path that keeps
Lord Momonosuke out of sight!

177
00:11:04.020 --> 00:11:06.690
Shogun! Come on out!

178
00:11:06.690 --> 00:11:09.520
Or else we'll bash the door in!

179
00:11:09.520 --> 00:11:11.150
– One, two!
– One, two!

180
00:11:14.110 --> 00:11:15.450
They're breaking through!

181
00:11:15.780 --> 00:11:17.030
Sorry, Momonosuke!

182
00:11:17.030 --> 00:11:18.030
What?!

183
00:11:18.030 --> 00:11:19.280
Hide in my clothes!

184
00:11:19.780 --> 00:11:20.780
What?

185
00:11:20.780 --> 00:11:21.870
Whaaat?!

186
00:11:34.420 --> 00:11:36.130
Let's go, Shinobu!

187
00:11:36.130 --> 00:11:38.840
I told you to keep him out of their sight!

188
00:11:40.470 --> 00:11:41.760
I know!

189
00:11:41.760 --> 00:11:44.140
They'll see him if we don't take them all down!

190
00:11:47.940 --> 00:11:50.150
That is not what I meant!

191
00:11:50.150 --> 00:11:51.820
– Damn you!
– Damn you!

192
00:11:56.110 --> 00:11:59.620
W-We Gifters have this route blocked already!

193
00:11:59.620 --> 00:12:01.830
You really shouldn't be fighting yet!

194
00:12:01.830 --> 00:12:03.290
Silence!

195
00:12:03.290 --> 00:12:04.870
Out of my way!

196
00:12:05.870 --> 00:12:07.000
Bao Huang!

197
00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:10.500
Are the Red Scabbards samurai
still in the treasury?

198
00:12:18.130 --> 00:12:20.140
Yes, they are!

199
00:12:20.140 --> 00:12:22.890
Black Maria! Where are you now?!

200
00:12:23.310 --> 00:12:25.600
I'm still in the banquet hall.

201
00:12:27.100 --> 00:12:31.440
Alright! I'll go and finish off those samurai!

202
00:12:36.780 --> 00:12:42.830
Even on the brink of death, there's
no way in hell the Soaring Six can kill them!

203
00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:46.700
Got it?! Stay out of this!

204
00:12:47.450 --> 00:12:48.790
Jack...

205
00:12:49.460 --> 00:12:52.540
You're underestimating me...

206
00:12:56.510 --> 00:12:57.670
Although...

207
00:12:59.220 --> 00:13:01.220
this works out in my favor.

208
00:13:03.180 --> 00:13:06.640
Sweet Entanglement

209
00:13:08.310 --> 00:13:11.440
I appreciate him taking care of that for me.

210
00:13:15.070 --> 00:13:17.030
What in the world... is that?

211
00:13:20.490 --> 00:13:22.490
Listen, Nico Robin...

212
00:13:23.530 --> 00:13:26.200
You'll belong to Viceroy Kaido soon...

213
00:13:27.490 --> 00:13:28.950
It's inevitable.

214
00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:32.080
No, thanks.

215
00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:34.290
I'd rather die!

216
00:13:35.250 --> 00:13:36.310
So cool!

217
00:13:49.890 --> 00:13:52.730
<b>Onigashima

Entrance</b>

218
00:14:01.900 --> 00:14:05.870
You gave it your best, full-moon warriors!

219
00:14:13.580 --> 00:14:17.540
Too bad the weather's not on your side!

220
00:14:23.930 --> 00:14:25.390
Pedro...

221
00:14:29.060 --> 00:14:30.430
Listen!

222
00:14:30.430 --> 00:14:33.850
You-gara must press on!

223
00:14:34.600 --> 00:14:38.440
No matter what... I have to avenge Pedro...!

224
00:14:41.860 --> 00:14:43.950
Avenge Pedro?!

225
00:14:43.950 --> 00:14:47.240
That worthless fool deserved to die!

226
00:14:48.200 --> 00:14:54.620
What was your plan after waltzing into
the Big Mom Pirates' territory? Have a picnic?!

227
00:14:55.790 --> 00:15:00.500
If you don't want your friends to die,
why don't you go back to grazing in the forest?!

228
00:15:07.260 --> 00:15:10.510
You can lick your wounds there!

229
00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:14.850
Now then...

230
00:15:14.850 --> 00:15:19.480
This alliance with the Beast Pirates
doesn't bring me a lick of excitement...

231
00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:22.900
but it's Mama's decision,
so I guess it can't be helped...

232
00:15:22.900 --> 00:15:28.910
We need to teach these kids that the
Four Emperors are way out of their league!

233
00:15:35.370 --> 00:15:36.830
They're running!

234
00:15:37.210 --> 00:15:40.840
The enemy leader Momonosuke...

235
00:15:40.840 --> 00:15:43.300
is moving away from...

236
00:15:43.630 --> 00:15:46.380
the Forbidden Storeroom!

237
00:15:57.270 --> 00:16:00.270
I cannot see Momonosuke at the moment!

238
00:16:00.900 --> 00:16:03.070
But there can be no doubt!

239
00:16:03.860 --> 00:16:08.990
Momonosuke is with Young Master
Yamato and the kunoichi!

240
00:16:13.950 --> 00:16:16.910
<b>Momonosuke

General of Wano's Samurai</b>

241
00:16:19.500 --> 00:16:24.000
It may be cramped and hard to breathe,
but for whatever reason...

242
00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:28.130
I feel as though I am in heaven!

243
00:16:36.310 --> 00:16:37.890
Shinobu, this way!

244
00:16:39.310 --> 00:16:40.900
They just keep coming!

245
00:16:44.820 --> 00:16:47.860
We need to find a less visible route!

246
00:16:47.860 --> 00:16:49.450
Don't worry!

247
00:16:49.450 --> 00:16:51.870
They can't see us if we take them all out!

248
00:16:51.870 --> 00:16:55.580
Like I told you, that is not what I meant!

249
00:17:00.170 --> 00:17:02.540
I repeat!

250
00:17:02.540 --> 00:17:06.960
Momonosuke, who escaped
from the Forbidden Storehouse,

251
00:17:02.580 --> 00:17:06.960
<b>Third Floor

Inside the Castle</b>

252
00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:11.180
is with Young Master Yamato
and the kunoichi!

253
00:17:11.180 --> 00:17:12.590
For certain!

254
00:17:13.050 --> 00:17:15.140
Another broadcast...

255
00:17:15.140 --> 00:17:17.270
They're going after Momo and Shinobu!

256
00:17:18.730 --> 00:17:19.980
Young Master Yamato?

257
00:17:20.730 --> 00:17:21.690
Well, whatever...

258
00:17:22.350 --> 00:17:25.230
Hey, which way is the Forbidden Storehouse?!

259
00:17:25.230 --> 00:17:26.980
L-Like I'm gonna tell you.

260
00:17:28.070 --> 00:17:28.940
Huh?!

261
00:17:30.360 --> 00:17:34.950
I-It's near the entrance of the Skull Dome...

262
00:17:37.290 --> 00:17:39.910
Kin'emon's group is at
the back of the castle tower...

263
00:17:38.120 --> 00:17:43.460
<b>Dome Entrance</b>
<b>Back of the Castle Tower</b>

264
00:17:40.460 --> 00:17:43.460
That's in the opposite direction
of the Dome's entrance.

265
00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:47.590
Kin'emon and the others are hurting bad...

266
00:17:48.420 --> 00:17:51.470
Momo and Shinobu are being
chased by the damn Gifters...

267
00:17:51.800 --> 00:17:53.840
Which of them needs me more?!

268
00:17:55.350 --> 00:17:57.350
This way?! That way?!

269
00:18:01.890 --> 00:18:03.940
No time to think!

270
00:18:03.940 --> 00:18:06.570
The ones who need me
the most are...

271
00:18:06.570 --> 00:18:08.470
definitely this way!

272
00:18:20.540 --> 00:18:21.790
I can't...

273
00:18:29.420 --> 00:18:33.180
This blue flame draws out my stamina, but...

274
00:18:33.970 --> 00:18:36.010
I think that I am...

275
00:18:36.390 --> 00:18:38.260
almost at my limit...

276
00:18:41.980 --> 00:18:45.440
Fight it! Or you'll turn into an ice ogre again!

277
00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:50.280
You'll lose control, use up the rest of your
energy, and die for sure this time!

278
00:18:52.820 --> 00:18:55.530
Don't give up, young man!

279
00:18:55.910 --> 00:18:58.240
Get a hold of yourself!

280
00:18:58.950 --> 00:19:03.910
That tanuki is suffering the same pain as you,
but he's still working hard on the antidote!

281
00:19:04.580 --> 00:19:07.290
How could we give up before him?

282
00:19:08.040 --> 00:19:10.300
B-Big Boss...

283
00:19:10.300 --> 00:19:12.300
You look different...

284
00:19:15.380 --> 00:19:18.470
Leave it to this old man!

285
00:19:21.850 --> 00:19:24.350
It's time to show them...

286
00:19:24.350 --> 00:19:27.190
a samurai's resilience!

287
00:19:31.650 --> 00:19:34.030
Apoo, we can't fight anymore!

288
00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:39.570
The antibody is right behind them, but we
just can't break through their ironclad defense!

289
00:19:39.570 --> 00:19:44.160
Why would His Awesomeness
infect us too?! We're on his side!

290
00:19:44.160 --> 00:19:48.040
He's not gonna save you no matter
how much you bitch and moan!

291
00:19:48.040 --> 00:19:53.090
Just kill that tanuki and get
the antibody already!

292
00:19:54.050 --> 00:19:55.130
Dammit!

293
00:19:55.470 --> 00:19:59.180
Drake! That traitor!

294
00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:02.390
Stop acting like a hero!

295
00:20:02.390 --> 00:20:05.140
Drake isn't the only problem!

296
00:20:05.850 --> 00:20:10.560
That withered old man recovered somehow!

297
00:20:11.860 --> 00:20:15.360
The legendary boss of Wano's underworld!

298
00:20:14.860 --> 00:20:18.360
<b>X Drake

Former Soaring Six Member
Saur-Saur Fruit: Allosaurus</b>
<b>Hyogoro "the Flower"

Legendary Boss of the Underworld</b>

299
00:20:16.320 --> 00:20:18.360
Hyogoro the Flower!

300
00:20:20.490 --> 00:20:23.450
With those two monsters standing guard...

301
00:20:23.830 --> 00:20:28.000
we have no chance of getting to that tanuki!

302
00:20:28.460 --> 00:20:30.540
Why does he look like that?!

303
00:20:30.540 --> 00:20:33.340
He was just a little old man a second ago!

304
00:20:33.340 --> 00:20:38.840
He's changed back into the tower of a man
that Kaido was dead set on recruiting!

305
00:20:41.340 --> 00:20:42.800
Shaking with excitement, huh?

306
00:20:43.510 --> 00:20:44.470
Big Boss!

307
00:20:44.850 --> 00:20:46.220
Are you okay?!

308
00:20:46.770 --> 00:20:48.100
Yeah...

309
00:20:48.810 --> 00:20:51.560
I can feel a chill... however...

310
00:20:52.690 --> 00:20:55.530
I still have faith in my spirit!

311
00:20:57.820 --> 00:21:00.820
I suppose catching this virus...

312
00:21:00.820 --> 00:21:05.790
drew out the last of my strength,
leaving me within an inch of death.

313
00:21:08.580 --> 00:21:10.790
So it's all come down to this...

314
00:21:12.290 --> 00:21:15.340
With my remaining power...

315
00:21:21.010 --> 00:21:24.010
even if it costs me my life...

316
00:21:24.010 --> 00:21:26.970
I will cut down every last one...

317
00:21:29.350 --> 00:21:31.480
of their major players!

318
00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:36.610
Hey! Underbosses!

319
00:21:36.610 --> 00:21:38.530
– Yes, Big Boss!
– Yes, Big Boss!

320
00:21:42.780 --> 00:21:46.330
I may not have much time left...

321
00:21:48.870 --> 00:21:55.960
If that tanuki can't finish the cure
and I turn into an ice ogre...

322
00:21:55.960 --> 00:21:57.500
Do one thing for me first!

323
00:21:59.380 --> 00:22:00.590
Don't hesitate...

324
00:22:01.380 --> 00:22:03.930
to strike me down!

325
00:22:05.550 --> 00:22:07.180
If you don't...

326
00:22:07.680 --> 00:22:10.180
I'll cut you all down...

327
00:22:10.180 --> 00:22:12.640
every last person—friend or foe—

328
00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:16.110
until no one is left!

329
00:22:16.900 --> 00:22:18.360
How can we...

330
00:22:18.360 --> 00:22:23.320
But... if the big boss becomes an ice ogre...

331
00:22:25.660 --> 00:22:28.370
nobody has a chance of stopping him...

332
00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:35.460
I'm counting on you...

333
00:22:36.790 --> 00:22:39.090
Alright then...

334
00:22:39.090 --> 00:22:43.630
As a former member of the Mimawari-gumi,
I'd like to see what he's got...

335
00:22:45.090 --> 00:22:47.800
You're some kind of legend, huh?

336
00:22:48.180 --> 00:22:50.680
All I see is a washed-up swordsman!

337
00:22:51.020 --> 00:22:53.140
You old fart!

338
00:22:54.060 --> 00:22:56.400
Prepare yourself!

339
00:23:14.460 --> 00:23:16.540
One-Sword Style of the Flower!

340
00:23:31.060 --> 00:23:32.560
Flaming Hair...

341
00:23:40.270 --> 00:23:41.440
of Holy Rage!

342
00:23:52.910 --> 00:23:57.620
<b>Flaming</b>

343
00:23:53.660 --> 00:23:57.620
<b>Hair of</b>

344
00:23:54.410 --> 00:23:57.620
<b>Holy</b>

345
00:23:54.910 --> 00:23:57.620
<b>Rage</b>

346
00:24:06.220 --> 00:24:09.840
Just throw bodies at him! Go!

347
00:24:18.230 --> 00:24:19.810
Hey, Oden...

348
00:24:23.270 --> 00:24:26.440
I sometimes wish...

349
00:24:30.160 --> 00:24:34.400
that we had challenged Kaido
back in the days...

350
00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:36.080
when we were at our peaks.

351
00:24:48.630 --> 00:24:49.550
But now...

352
00:24:50.000 --> 00:24:51.590
Kin'emon and the others...

353
00:24:51.590 --> 00:24:54.560
have pulled off the perfect raid!

354
00:24:58.140 --> 00:24:59.350
Furthermore...

355
00:24:59.890 --> 00:25:03.440
I have gained a most interesting disciple!

356
00:25:11.570 --> 00:25:13.320
Sir Straw Hat!

357
00:25:13.320 --> 00:25:15.620
You have great potential.

358
00:25:16.330 --> 00:25:19.040
You will continue to grow
stronger and stronger!

359
00:25:19.540 --> 00:25:21.120
Remember this.

360
00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:22.670
In a moment of crisis...

361
00:25:23.960 --> 00:25:26.170
your true power will be revealed!

362
00:25:33.180 --> 00:25:35.600
Let us take down Kaido together!

363
00:25:39.560 --> 00:25:40.770
You got it!

364
00:25:41.100 --> 00:25:43.610
Using that ryuo you taught me...

365
00:25:44.440 --> 00:25:48.150
I'll kick Kaido's ass!

366
00:25:49.690 --> 00:25:53.910
There was neither a hint of deception
nor conceit in those words.

367
00:25:54.280 --> 00:25:58.290
I'm certain he'll master ryuo,
grow even stronger...

368
00:25:59.620 --> 00:26:02.080
and finally take down Kaido!

369
00:26:02.870 --> 00:26:05.040
Keep watching, Oden!

370
00:26:10.010 --> 00:26:12.130
I know in my heart that the land of Wano...

371
00:26:14.220 --> 00:26:16.220
will see the dawn once again!

372
00:26:18.470 --> 00:26:20.230
Whoa there!

373
00:26:20.230 --> 00:26:22.390
The whole floor is gonna get wiped out!

374
00:26:26.440 --> 00:26:30.320
Time to meet your maker, you old fool!

375
00:26:31.530 --> 00:26:33.360
Phoenix Brand!

376
00:26:40.910 --> 00:26:43.960
You better keep your eyes on me, Queen!

377
00:26:45.790 --> 00:26:47.670
Marco!

378
00:26:47.670 --> 00:26:49.500
That hurt!

379
00:26:49.500 --> 00:26:51.960
Was that a shockwave
or something, you punk?!

380
00:26:52.260 --> 00:26:54.970
I'm the one you're fighting right now!

381
00:26:54.970 --> 00:26:58.390
You can focus on attacking those samurai...

382
00:26:58.390 --> 00:27:00.850
after you chop off my head!

383
00:27:00.850 --> 00:27:05.150
Dammit! This guy just won't die!

384
00:27:07.610 --> 00:27:10.530
Go to hell already!

385
00:27:27.080 --> 00:27:29.420
Bluebird!

386
00:27:51.690 --> 00:27:54.070
Time to finish you off!

387
00:27:54.490 --> 00:27:56.400
You son of a bitch!

388
00:27:57.240 --> 00:27:59.950
Don't push your luck!

389
00:28:03.160 --> 00:28:04.500
Crane Talons!

390
00:28:19.340 --> 00:28:26.730
Guess it's no surprise... Holding off
a couple guys worth over a billion ain't easy...

391
00:28:32.650 --> 00:28:35.070
You bastard!

392
00:28:47.250 --> 00:28:49.790
Come on already, tanuki...!

393
00:28:53.630 --> 00:28:58.470
What's this? Is that Marco I spy over there?

394
00:28:58.470 --> 00:29:01.590
Seems like he's taken a real...

395
00:29:02.890 --> 00:29:04.390
licking.

396
00:29:06.930 --> 00:29:09.730
Everyone's turning back into ice ogres!

397
00:29:09.730 --> 00:29:12.060
Th-The fire's gone...

398
00:29:12.060 --> 00:29:13.690
Help me!

399
00:29:24.330 --> 00:29:26.700
Do it! This is what I want!

400
00:29:35.460 --> 00:29:39.380
It's as if the heavens themselves
have granted me one final reward...

401
00:29:39.920 --> 00:29:43.820
I was rotting away in a cell,
just waiting to die,

402
00:29:43.820 --> 00:29:45.600
and yet I made it all the way here...

403
00:29:51.520 --> 00:29:56.690
However, if I continue to live,
all of your lives are at risk!

404
00:29:56.690 --> 00:30:00.110
Forgive me for putting you in this position...

405
00:30:00.110 --> 00:30:02.200
but you must do this for me!

406
00:30:11.960 --> 00:30:15.040
The rest of you will have to
carry on in my stead...

407
00:30:16.670 --> 00:30:19.420
The man known as Hyogoro the Flower...

408
00:30:23.180 --> 00:30:25.300
leaves this world...

409
00:30:26.140 --> 00:30:28.480
with no regrets!
